.TH "RTCTRANSPORTSTATS.DTLSCIPHER" "3JS" "June 24, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCTransportStats.dtlsCipher \- RTCTransportStats: dtlsCipher property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]dtlsCipher\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCTransportStats\f[R] dictionary is a string that indicates the
descriptive name of the cipher suite used for the DTLS transport.
.PP
Allowed names are defined in the \(lqDescription\(rq column of the \c
.UR https://www.iana.org/assignments/tls-parameters/tls-parameters.xhtml#table-tls-parameters-4
TLS Cipher Suites
.UE \c
\ section in the \f[I]IANA cipher suite registry\f[R].
For example \f[CR]\(dqTLS_ECDHE_ECDSA_WITH_AES_128_GCM_SHA256\(dq\f[R].
.SH VALUE
A string indicating the name of the DTLS cipher.
